  "title": "HR Business Partner (Manufacturing US Firm) #JTL",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible for payroll & CPF contributions for all employees under Singapore / Malaysia employment.</li><li>Advertising and sourcing of available positions.</li><li>Arranging interviews, screening, and trainings where necessary.</li><li>Ensuring all government regulations regarding foreign hires are followed.</li><li>Guiding Workers through onboarding orientations and exit interviews.</li><li>Ensuring new hires are in the Facial Recognition System.</li><li>Prepare and compile HR and other ad-hoc reports.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or Degree in Human Resource Management or Business Management.  </li><li>Minimum 3 years of HR generalist experience.</li><li>Able to work in Tuas area. </li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</strong><br /><strong>Topaz Liang Huimin (CEI No. R1104500), email to: topaz@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong><br /><strong>EA License No. 99C4599</strong></p>",
